medications.name: Sertraline
medications.response: Minimal improvement noted after 4 weeks; patient reports persistent low mood, anhedonia, and early morning awakening.

changes_made.rationale: Inadequate clinical response (persistent anhedonia, guilt, passive SI) after 4 weeks at the initial therapeutic dose. Dose increased from 50mg daily to 100mg daily to optimize treatment efficacy for *Recurrent Major Depressive Disorder*.
